import React from 'react';
import { Col, Button, Form, FormGroup, Label, Input, FormText } from 'reactstrap';
import '../../../Styles/JoinForm/JoinForm.css'

export default class Example extends React.Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <Form>
        <FormGroup row>
          <Label for="exampleEmail" id="join-form__label" sm={2}>Email</Label>
          <Col sm={10}>
            <Input type="email" name="email" id="join-form__input" placeholder="johndoe@example.com" />
          </Col>
        </FormGroup>
        <FormGroup row>
          <Label for="exampleSelect" id="join-form__label" sm={2}>Company Type</Label>
          <Col sm={10}>
            <Input type="select" name="select" id="join-form__input" />
          </Col>
        </FormGroup>
        <FormGroup row>
          <Label for="exampleText" id="join-form__label" sm={2}>Company Description</Label>
          <Col sm={10}>
            <Input type="textarea" name="text" id="join-form__input" placeholder='Tell us about yourself...' />
          </Col>
        </FormGroup>
        <FormGroup check row>
          <Col sm={{ size: 10, offset: 2 }}>
            <Button>Submit</Button>
          </Col>
        </FormGroup>
      </Form>
    );
  }
}
